[SN]TITLE[SN]
Football is all about winning - Gordon Strachan

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Scotland manager Gordon Strachan rejects the idea that young footballers should play with no regard for the score.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
